articles.title: About this blog
articles.description: Quinten's thoughts about life the universe and everything. Ideas in development, not for commercial use.
articles.contents:
This site is one part a development and coding project, one part a journal of my thoughts and one part a mystery even to me. My hope is that I capture some part of what it means to be Quinten Giglio and this blog is a practice and ritual of growth and expression.
